{"tid":1020984,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【互動故】我要捱過今個情人節！","createTime":"2019-02-14T03:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T14:12:39.000Z","uid":140830,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"711ec95ce4583df04976a5db59a8cfe4a5ca2c18","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:14:15.000Z","msg":"一覺醒來，我揉著沉重的眼睛滑開手機，顯示時間：2019年2月14日，上午八時零一分。<br />\n<br />\n我躺了下來，對著天花板重重嘆了口氣。今天對單身狗如我，注定是一年中最難過的一天。<br />\n<br />\n哼，沒情人又怎樣？我自己一個也可以活得好端端的⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我的腦子這樣想著，身體卻很誠實，一時之間悲從中來，在房間慟哭大叫：<br />\n<br />\n「天啊！我求下你！可唔可以賜個大波長腿嘅靚女俾我啊！」<br />\n<br />\n沒有任何反應。<br />\n<br />\n那是當然，這是現實生活，不是奇幻愛情片。如果每個毒男大喝一聲都有女溝的話，網上就不會有那麼叫春post ，世上就不會再有強姦案。<br />\n<br />\n我恥笑了自己一聲，這麼大個人了，居然還有這麼好笑的想法。<br />\n<br />\n日子難過但總要過，接下來要就甚麼才好呢？"},{"pid":"5ad06fc9bb1cfbc1304e535b86eca2f9845dfd3f","tid":1020984,"uid":99364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:15:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c9ee6ea9c0f51fa82faf83c83a331900fcece06","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"A. 起身返大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nB. 繼續訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d887cbd7011ba4520bb1bc0a14779a36769bd2","tid":1020984,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:16:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b8eef6d4888cffcb23720d9997faec893ddcddb","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ad06fc9bb1cfbc1304e535b86eca2f9845dfd3f","tid":1020984,"uid":99364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:15:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kS7hKfs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkS7hKfs.gif&h=aa93e017&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8afdc9b4c29a0b02024eb5918b7f83b59b424c42","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"選擇以第一個回覆為準<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同時更新會比較慢，唔好見怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為係即叫即寫"},{"pid":"fd04cb64aef0c907719aec74676db006d946c52d","tid":1020984,"uid":3549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"52d887cbd7011ba4520bb1bc0a14779a36769bd2","tid":1020984,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c9ee6ea9c0f51fa82faf83c83a331900fcece06","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"A. 起身返大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nB. 繼續訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:16:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"2019年2月15日，上午八時零一分<br />\n終於捱過今個情人節<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b305aa3f1b92a4a757c53501ac03dede578e9b52","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52d887cbd7011ba4520bb1bc0a14779a36769bd2","tid":1020984,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c9ee6ea9c0f51fa82faf83c83a331900fcece06","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"A. 起身返大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nB. 繼續訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:16:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"我望一望自己個schedule，原來今日要上十半堂，我計一計時間，而家起身食埋個早餐再施施然行返去的話，時間其實非常充足。<br />\n<br />\n但我忽然醒起我個friend 阿強嘅一句至理名言：「痴線㗎！？上到大學仲返學！？你有冇良知㗎！？只有廢柴先會努力讀書㗎咋！我理得你讀到曉飛咪又係出嚟考ACO！」<br />\n<br />\n於是我下定決心，返去繼續覺覺豬。<br />\n<br />\n點知我一撻返落床，就有人㩒響咗個門鐘。<br />\n<br />\n「妖！邊個啊？」<br />\n<br />\n我懷住不耐煩嘅心情打開大門，一張白皙甜美的臉蛋隨即映入眼簾。<br />\n<br />\n係、係、係女仔！？？？？<br />\n<br />\n我望住眼前嘅女仔呆咗半秒。<br />\n<br />\n「Hello，你好啊⋯⋯請問你呢度係咪⋯⋯啊啊啊啊！」個女仔望一望我之後發出悽厲慘叫，喂大佬雖然我「高大靚仔」入面淨係中咗「仔」呢個字，但都唔駛好似見到怪物咁啩。<br />\n<br />\n但我望一望自己，OH SHIT！我唔記得自己冇著衫𠻹！<br />\n<br />\n我意識到之後火速關門。平時我都習慣咗裸睡，喺屋企都唔著衫，點知道突然間會有客人嚟㗎啫？<br />\n<br />\n我喺雜亂不堪嘅衣櫃入面摷返幾件見得下人嘅衫之後，再睇睇個防盜眼，原來個女仔仲喺度。<br />\n<br />\n我深呼吸之後再次開門，然後口窒窒咁講：「唔、唔好意思⋯⋯頭先未準備好！」<br />\n<br />\n點知佢忽然雙眼一亮，眼甘甘打量我全身，說：「唔係啊⋯⋯我覺得你都幾⋯⋯好吖。係啦，請問你係咪就係傳說中嗰個捉鬼大師？」<br />\n<br />\n我見佢望住部手機咁問我，我就知道佢搵錯路先上咗嚟。<br />\n<br />\n但我見到佢無辜嘅眼神，一副求助心切嘅神色，雪白修長嘅大腿加上唔知CDEF 嘅波濤洶湧，成個雞扒妹咁嘅樣，一時之間確實拿不定主意。"},{"pid":"7b5da94fe71a3c69e5d232cd6f68e0ebe9c513f1","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"A。9吹自己係捉鬼大師，請佢入屋<br />\n<br />\nB。嘭門收佢皮<br />\n<br />\nC。上連登開PO 問點算"},{"pid":"7aa3a0d69a29a15a7fa4624b102ea5ece19f00b9","tid":1020984,"uid":62822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b093207c99e39fea838490d941ffcbcc9aea5dca","tid":1020984,"uid":129142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:18:14.000Z","msg":"A <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee596226879a481f90d295e3131f32fc72244732","tid":1020984,"uid":228854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:20:37.000Z","msg":"LM 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da5c27e98870b2466963532e81855602a0b996f","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee596226879a481f90d295e3131f32fc72244732","tid":1020984,"uid":228854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:20:37.000Z","msg":"LM 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"又係你啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f10d5e4d26ed54b9a3d3662a08df592924550c","tid":1020984,"uid":127164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T04:46:12.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"3fd8ba3968a453f1fae6338af0db8afee2b7ce92","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:03:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「求助」有條女問我係咪捉鬼大師！</span><br />\n<br />\n我受驚過度之下又閂埋咗門，急急腳上連登向各位身高米八，DSE 30 分，巨龍30cm，FG 人工五萬嘅連登仔求助。<br />\n<br />\n連登不愧係網絡清泉，每個會員都好熱於助人，我好快就收到佢哋嘅留言：<br />\n<br />\n「假膠唔駛理。」<br />\n<br />\n「樓主現實一定係日日喺屋企打機嘅廢青，日日寫埋啲廢文。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n「幾廿歲人唔好FF咁多，傷身。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n「冇圖學人開PO！有老母都冇用啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n我諗諗下發覺自己都有啲唔啱，於是UP咗呢張圖上去：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lh8wPhv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLh8wPhv.jpg&h=9baee15e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「大概係咁。」<br />\n<br />\n放完圖之後我頓覺身心舒暢，大抵這就是完成了作為一個樓主應有的責任時所帶來的愉悅吧。<br />\n<br />\n而全能嘅連登仔喺見到張圖之後，亦都俾出一個相當有用嘅答案：<br />\n<br />\n「此帖已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n我突然為自己有「上連登求助」這個想法覺得可笑。"},{"pid":"4a951b1c5863f4b739733d72d70ecbcb6bcf3bb3","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:04:14.000Z","msg":"繼續<br />\n<br />\nA。9吹自己係捉鬼大師，請佢入屋<br />\n<br />\nB。嘭門收佢皮"},{"pid":"53a024e1e070298bf7b569c39fd252b03162f00f","tid":1020984,"uid":137042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a951b1c5863f4b739733d72d70ecbcb6bcf3bb3","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:04:14.000Z","msg":"繼續<br />\n<br />\nA。9吹自己係捉鬼大師，請佢入屋<br />\n<br />\nB。嘭門收佢皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:16:07.000Z","msg":"A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cf26333dbd5e835cd51a9f2c4ed32b4d866c95","tid":1020984,"uid":129142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:51:49.000Z","msg":"A <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e7b99c734883f6ee3730442b470b1cb0667347","tid":1020984,"uid":228854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"A<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd22724db20630967da2fdffd7a0340a5a32b16","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:13:09.000Z","msg":"剪緊髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陣間寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f2b6bf7f5a5bb2e61dab791bc0cd0c8531d70e","tid":1020984,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"樓主一路屌閪一路打文，而觀眾仍天真地幻想。"},{"pid":"7d409c97f0821450f9c9f2918baf6b2fb6a27703","tid":1020984,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16f2b6bf7f5a5bb2e61dab791bc0cd0c8531d70e","tid":1020984,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"樓主一路屌閪一路打文，而觀眾仍天真地幻想。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:20:39.000Z","msg":"我都想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e2d55bf5af53c65cf54790586084b83263adc1","tid":1020984,"uid":228854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:10:10.000Z","msg":"情人節就嚟完啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6eda8399704504d61a1e69c8ab2109288c571b6","tid":1020984,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4e2d55bf5af53c65cf54790586084b83263adc1","tid":1020984,"uid":228854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep